Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.31,0:01:34.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.49,0:01:40.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  那又為什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.02,0:01:45.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  我覺得石動同學很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.53,0:01:47.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我被她給看透了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.43,0:02:08.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被她給看透了…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.37,0:02:11.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被看透了什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.18,0:02:28.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雞的餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.49,0:02:36.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早啊  真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.68,0:02:42.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,討厭  朋與你真奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.23,0:02:45.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,今天也去「小愛」吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.95,0:02:47.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.82,0:02:58.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.63,0:03:01.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  借我下英語字典
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.28,0:03:04.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  就放在櫥櫃裡
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.97,0:03:05.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我就借走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.59,0:03:09.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:11.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.89,0:03:13.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  野伏
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.79,0:03:19.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.00,0:03:21.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.11,0:03:32.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個例題是積分基礎中的基礎
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.50,0:03:37.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望大家理解到很容易就能解開
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.70,0:03:44.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪嗎  給你那紅果的人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.39,0:03:45.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.87,0:03:48.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就是愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.61,0:03:51.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅果的數量表達了愛你的程度
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.56,0:03:54.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得自己被她接二連三地詛咒了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.13,0:03:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.29,0:04:01.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,詛咒的源頭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.08,0:04:05.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.69,0:04:07.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  不錯嘛  放學後的約會？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.41,0:04:09.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是去抱怨幾句而已
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.01,0:04:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心不要被她吃掉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.96,0:04:14.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蠢材
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.71,0:04:20.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙搞什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.67,0:04:23.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.03,0:04:32.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是石動乃繪？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.86,0:04:36.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,騎摩托車來接她？  好低級
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.61,0:04:56.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小愛～
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.49,0:04:59.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦  真一郎呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:01.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他說過會兒就來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.51,0:05:03.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.14,0:05:06.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要送去文化館的慰問品
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.35,0:05:08.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像非常好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.39,0:05:10.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  餵我一個
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:12.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.71,0:05:15.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  快餵我
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.99,0:05:28.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我要唉聲歎氣的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:31.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼回事啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.72,0:05:39.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們在幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.86,0:05:44.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只是在嘗味道
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.73,0:05:46.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.87,0:05:51.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,快點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.90,0:06:04.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,再靠近一點
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:05.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.34,0:06:12.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.36,0:06:16.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去拿喝的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.66,0:06:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還真是喜歡吃掉了的東西啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.38,0:06:23.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要是小愛的料理  就算掉在地上我也會吃掉
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.66,0:06:25.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣很快會吃壞肚子哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.41,0:06:27.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,吃小愛的料理而死是正合我意的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.01,0:06:33.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪有男朋友？  真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.27,0:06:34.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.35,0:06:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那她為什麼要調戲你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.43,0:06:42.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她只是想要我代替雷轟丸而已
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.41,0:06:44.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,雷轟丸？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.29,0:06:46.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,後庭的一隻雞
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻雞死掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.64,0:06:54.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,難不成那些紅果是？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.33,0:06:56.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那隻雞的餌食
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.24,0:06:59.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是被圈養的雞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.01,0:07:01.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,才沒有被圈養
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.01,0:07:04.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎  時間到了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.13,0:07:07.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不好  我也得回家了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.85,0:07:19.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不早了啊  抄近路吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.23,0:07:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.59,0:07:24.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.33,0:07:27.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼樣了  前幾天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.79,0:07:28.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.48,0:07:29.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小美的事
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.45,0:07:31.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你打聽了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.88,0:07:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我是聽說到的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.70,0:07:35.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.60,0:07:40.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她說想和乃繪做朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.62,0:07:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實不是那樣的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.48,0:07:46.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯  好像是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.85,0:07:52.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得可以理解
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.25,0:07:53.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.38,0:07:56.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她為什麼會說那種話
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.19,0:07:59.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我不告訴你
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.72,0:08:02.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  那算什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.61,0:08:03.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.64,0:08:05.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉  不小心就…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.36,0:08:09.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,東西很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.91,0:08:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我來拿吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.86,0:08:11.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人這種動物…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.76,0:08:23.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人這種動物一旦喜歡上別人  就會想更靠近對方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.64,0:08:27.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想更加更加靠近那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.14,0:08:30.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  當那個想法無法實現時
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.80,0:08:33.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就會想待在那個人附近的某個人身邊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.84,0:08:36.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,某個人？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.62,0:08:50.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喜歡上像你這種人的女孩  真是可憐
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.16,0:08:53.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼  好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.43,0:08:59.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比如說  比呂美喜歡上了某人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.15,0:09:03.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為想要靠近那個人而待在乃繪身邊…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.07,0:09:05.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個某人是誰啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,乃繪身邊的男人…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.39,0:09:09.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.06,0:09:12.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.69,0:09:16.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  也沒有別人了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.31,0:09:19.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不會吧  不
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.29,0:09:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼可能…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.54,0:09:23.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可是  說不定…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.53,0:09:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,晚上好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.68,0:09:33.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少爺  腰再低一點
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.78,0:09:34.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.09,0:09:42.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來  少爺
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.30,0:09:44.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.11,0:09:45.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.92,0:09:47.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.80,0:09:49.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你好像很高興啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.57,0:09:53.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉部運動
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.27,0:09:58.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,把嘴做橫向運動  對健康有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.62,0:10:00.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉部運動…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.09,0:10:03.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真不錯呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.79,0:10:06.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臉部運動嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.35,0:10:16.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}被拜託了的  希望你能送去
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.42,0:10:21.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}你千萬不要對對方失敬  明白了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:21.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我回來了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.26,0:10:22.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎回來
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.67,0:10:24.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.29,0:10:26.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪裡嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.02,0:10:29.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是急事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.91,0:10:33.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送給船主大叔慶祝的酒
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.52,0:10:36.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事明天去辦不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.61,0:10:37.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在都這麼晚了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.28,0:10:40.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說好了要在今天送去的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.52,0:10:42.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那我去了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:45.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.35,0:10:46.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走咯
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.70,0:10:55.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.89,0:10:57.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他們兩個出門了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.69,0:11:00.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,送東西去大叔那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.98,0:11:03.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明明用不著連阿真也一塊兒去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.66,0:11:06.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那樣的話  讓真一郎去不就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.12,0:11:08.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓阿真去…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.06,0:11:09.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼讓比呂美去？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.64,0:11:11.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,比呂美已經是我們家的孩子了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.28,0:11:13.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和真一郎一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.91,0:11:15.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她不是我的孩子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.97,0:11:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.51,0:11:31.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你沒必要跟我來的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.86,0:11:35.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這條路暗下來後很危險的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.43,0:11:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,而且酒瓶也很重吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.32,0:11:42.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不用太在意的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.58,0:11:45.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,又不是傭人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.66,0:11:46.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我受了你家的照顧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:50.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了  這條路我們以前走過的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.87,0:11:54.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,祭典的時候  和你走散了  哭得哇哇的呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.76,0:11:57.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不記得了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.63,0:12:01.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.14,0:12:04.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  關於昨天的事
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.53,0:12:08.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你說被看透了…  那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.26,0:12:13.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  其實我很害怕走這條路的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.01,0:12:16.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎  說的也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.21,0:12:38.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.70,0:12:40.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我  真一郎君
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.90,0:14:05.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我全都封印在心裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.33,0:14:08.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當決定在這個家生活的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.03,0:14:22.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要丟下我…嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.18,0:14:28.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然說不記得了  真受打擊啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.56,0:14:33.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  即便只是在一起走走也是進步了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.87,0:14:41.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我希望你能抓緊我  於是伸出了手
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就在那時  天空慢慢飄起了雪
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.62,0:14:50.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,紅色  鮮紅的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.37,0:14:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不可思議的雪
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.84,0:15:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好苦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.24,0:15:22.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好冷
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.60,0:15:33.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.84,0:15:37.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經這麼晚了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.93,0:15:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我今天要去準備男籃的比賽
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.84,0:15:43.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊  是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.44,0:15:44.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,過會兒見
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.30,0:15:45.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.05,0:15:45.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.16,0:15:46.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.51,0:15:49.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我有時間的話會去加油的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.79,0:15:50.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.82,0:15:54.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.74,0:15:58.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我再去睡一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.86,0:16:12.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,螢川的男籃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.89,0:16:14.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有什麼打算
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.61,0:16:17.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,反正也沒別的事  去看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.33,0:16:18.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說  仲上君
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.40,0:16:20.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.15,0:16:22.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是仲上君的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.17,0:16:24.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？  什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.01,0:16:28.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  這個是…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.80,0:16:29.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.33,0:16:32.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.69,0:16:34.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這東西一直連過去的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.35,0:16:37.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那～傢～伙～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:40.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.97,0:16:46.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  她在想什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.52,0:16:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.86,0:16:57.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:17:00.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,都說了我不需要紅果
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.69,0:17:02.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這可不是你說了算的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你啊  我不知道你怎麼想的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.43,0:17:08.93,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過你還是不要和我扯上關係比較好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.45,0:17:09.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.46,0:17:12.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你有男朋友的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.33,0:17:13.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.57,0:17:14.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和你在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.40,0:17:19.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你別再纏著我了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.43,0:17:21.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等  我下不來了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.46,0:17:22.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你自己爬上去的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.11,0:17:24.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那就自己下來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.63,0:17:32.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好疼…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.26,0:17:35.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你啊
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.72,0:17:43.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好啦  站起來
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.94,0:17:46.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你幹什麼啊  喂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.50,0:17:51.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂就在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,蟑螂就在真一郎的腦子裡
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.34,0:18:05.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真一郎的背後也有蟑螂
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.20,0:18:05.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.80,0:18:07.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真輕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.06,0:18:08.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.76,0:18:11.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼那邊？  你…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.75,0:18:13.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊是哪裡你知道嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.00,0:18:14.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.16,0:18:18.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說你  你的腳真疼假疼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.08,0:18:44.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8\fs22}那邊  那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:04.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.61,0:19:05.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,到這裡就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.24,0:19:07.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的腳…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.10,0:19:07.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼！？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.63,0:19:12.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在幹什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.82,0:19:13.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是那傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.33,0:19:15.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個4號
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.48,0:19:17.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙是乃繪的…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.63,0:19:18.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哥哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.06,0:19:20.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是哥哥啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.76,0:19:21.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.73,0:19:22.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,老哥？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.02,0:19:24.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,加油
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.10,0:19:47.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,誤以為她老哥是男朋友了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.66,0:19:49.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,算了  常有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.90,0:19:50.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.93,0:19:52.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那首先你就該確認一下啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.22,0:19:57.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙有沒有男朋友  跟我又沒有關係
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.74,0:19:59.54,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但你卻鬆了口氣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.67,0:20:00.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,胡說八道
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.55,0:20:03.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,也是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.06,0:20:10.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,畢竟你有湯淺比呂美了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.69,0:20:12.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別擅自決定了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.67,0:20:14.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你還是找個理由比較好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.91,0:20:15.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.79,0:20:17.06,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你背石動乃繪的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.47,0:20:19.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才被她看得一清二楚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.92,0:20:22.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看見那個肯定會誤會的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.76,0:20:25.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼我非得找理由不可啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.83,0:20:32.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你先回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.19,0:20:39.36,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起  麻煩你把球扔過來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.79,0:20:40.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.49,0:20:43.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,剛才的你看見了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.58,0:20:46.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個傻瓜在想些什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.04,0:20:48.97,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,與我無關啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.31,0:20:50.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.66,0:20:52.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  這樣下去真的不要緊嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.40,0:20:54.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂  比呂美
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.79,0:20:57.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,其實你喜歡仲上君不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.58,0:21:01.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,石動乃繪的腳受傷了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.45,0:21:05.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我和那傢伙之間沒什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.05,0:21:08.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她突然就從樹上跳了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.65,0:21:14.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什麼啊  這不搞得好像真發生過什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.72,0:21:15.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.63,0:21:19.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我放棄  我放棄  我放棄  我放棄…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.47,0:21:20.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說謊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:23.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.50,0:21:26.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種事我不會對朋與你說謊的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.16,0:21:35.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我喜歡的是螢川的4號
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.94,0:21:37.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.27,0:21:41.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:42.80,0:21:46.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所以你不要再提真一郎君的名字了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.56,0:23:43.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,原來…你是這麼健談的啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.47,0:23:48.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個  難不成你在躲著我？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.03,0:23:50.65,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和乃繪交往吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.63,0:23:53.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來 眼睛眨一眨
